messages.text: Hey! Did you get that pic I sent you??
ya. i meant 2 talk 2 u bout that.
I’m about to send you another!
Yes…why are you so adamant about it?
who’s that man n the pic
that pic ur talkin about, there’s a man in it
No there isn’t! You are crazy! Hahaha
im lookin at it right now, there is a man in the right corner just standin there, blank face, with a black suit on
I’m looking at it too and all I can see is me and the Eiffel tower. Hahaha
Maybe there’s someone in the crowd that you’re seeing.
Whateves, I’m sending you another pic right now!
just b careful k? whoever that is looks creepy…
Did you get the second photo?
Beautiful huh?!?!? I love this place! I could live here.
See how the sunset reflects off the river? Unlike anything in America!
That first man you thought was in with me at the Eiffel tower??
Are you trying to scare me?? Hahah. Or play a joke!
look! On the bank of the river
ya, on the other side. same guy in a suit…
hes n the same stance wit the same look
You trying to ruin my trip?? Hahah
Or are you jealous that I went without me??
when did u take those pics?
Yesterday! I’m just out and about today. Nothing special.
maybe im just seein things, but I swear..
I’m looking at the same pics and see nothing.
Yes!! Cindy! Why’re you acting so weird?! You’re making me paranoid!!
u took those pics yesterday u said? and ur ok today?
Stop making me paranoid!! I’m enjoying France so far, don’t make me doubt that!
Went to the Notre Dame cathedral the first day, then Pont Alexandre the second, and yesterday I just walked the city.
It was awesome! Oh! I have pics of those too!
idk if id trust sending pics 2 me
I’m not in these, so maybe this ‘man’ won’t be there. Haha
I know you can’t prolly tell, but its HUGE in person.
CINDY! U HAVE SOMEONE FOLLOWING U!!!
the man… same guy, same suit and face, standing near the entrance…
and hes standing by the lightpost on the bridge…
I’m gonna stop txting you if you keep claiming there is a man.
It was funny at first, but now it’s just too much.
You really are starting to make me not enjoy my trip so much.
really! have u known me 2 joke around??
im really worried, i swear i see him in every pic
Seriously. I’m not going to contact you if you keep this up.
do u really not see anything n these pics?
NO! I looked them over and over, but I see nothing! Trust me. You’ve made me scared!!
Are you going to keep this up?? Or can we have a conversation without you patronizing me.
Is it cause you’re jealous I’m here? Do you wanna visit that bad??
as long as ur ok and feel safe…
I’d send you a pic, but…
Yeah right. You’re just gonna say there’s someone there.
only if there is… I’m actually concerned for you.
Oh my… You’re still on this…
im lookin back on these pics now…
ur gonna get mad at wat i say…
Oh my gosh… I’m done txting you. See you when you get back.
I do feel like there is someone here??
wat do u mean?!?! do u see him?
I think. Wait. Who is that??
Ha! Now you know how it feels.
I was kidding with you like you were me.
Whatever. Bye until I get back.
wait!! Keep txting me so I know ur still safe!
One last pic of what you’re missing…
